author: veithen
msg: Merged NamedNodeMapImpl and AttributeMap (which extended NamedNodeMapImpl) into a single class.

Rationale: DOM uses NamedNodeMap for entities (entity declarations, not entity references), notations and attributes. DOOM will likely never support retrieving entities and notations from the DTD and we therefore don't need NamedNodeMapImpl as a separate class.
